- ✅ `GetHashCode()` delegates to `Bits.GetHashCode()` — no boxing
- ✅ `TryParseWithSuffix` uses `StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase` — correct
- ✅ `ByteSymbol`/`BitSymbol` `.Contains()` uses `StringComparison.Ordinal` (L212, L218)

